media:group.media:title: Finnish For Beginners :small words
media:group.media:description:
Finnish For Beginners: Do you know some "small words" in Finnish?  In this lesson we’ll be looking at some  small words in Finnish and sentences with further explanations of these words and their use :) for example No niin! Which means *SO* which in this context is often said just before you’re about to do something and “lhan tosi” means really.
